ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
UsePAM no
PrintMotd no
X11Forwarding no
AllowTcpForwarding no
AllowAgentForwarding no
PermitTunnel no
 
Subsystem sftp internal-sftp
Match Group sftp
    ChrootDirectory /data
    X11Forwarding no
    AllowTcpForwarding no
    AllowAgentForwarding no
    PermitTunnel no
    ForceCommand internal-sftp -e
